The paper deals with algorithmic fairness in allocation problems, which involves learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the policing problem, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
